  "description": "<ul><li>🌟 We’re Hiring: Restaurant Food Runner 🌟</li></ul><p>📍 HarbourFront MRT (NE1 – Purple Line)</p><ul><li>🏢 Industry: Food Services (Chain Restaurant)</li></ul><p>💰 Salary & Benefits</p><ul><li>Basic Salary: SGD 3,000</li><li>Monthly Off Days: 6 days</li><li>Meal Allowance</li><li>Annual Company Trip</li><li>Team-Building Activities</li><li>Annual & Sick Leave: In accordance with MOM regulations</li></ul><p>⸻ ⏰ Working Hours</p><ul><li>9:30 AM – 2:00 PM</li><li>4:30 PM – 10:00 PM</li></ul><p>(Comfortable split shift in a fully air-conditioned working environment)</p><p>⸻ 🍽 About the Role We are a well-established chain restaurant offering a positive and supportive working environment. We are looking for an experienced Restaurant Food Runner to support our service team and ensure smooth food delivery during operations.</p><p>⸻ 🔑 Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Deliver food orders accurately and promptly to customers to ensure timely service</li><li>Collaborate with service staff to maintain smooth restaurant operations during shifts</li><li>Clean and organize service areas to uphold hygiene and operational standards</li><li>Adhere to company standards and operational procedures to maintain consistent service quality</li></ul><p>⸻ ✅ Required Competencies</p><ul><li>Demonstrate prior experience in the food & beverage industry to perform core duties effectively</li><li>Apply attention to detail and responsibility to ensure accurate order delivery and service support</li><li>Work efficiently in a fast-paced food and beverage environment to meet operational demands</li><li>Exhibit teamwork and maintain a positive work attitude to support colleagues and customer service</li><li>Comply with work arrangements and schedules as required by the employer</li></ul><p>⸻ ✨ If you enjoy working in a dynamic restaurant environment and want to be part of a reputable F&B brand, apply now and join our team!</p><p>⸻ We are a Manpower, Recruitment and Employment Agency that provides reliable and tailored staffing solutions. We do our very best to ensure that our candidates are looked-after and given the opportunity to attain their career goals.</p>",
